<NomaiObject>
	<TextBlock>
		<ID>1</ID>
		<Text>SECCA: Our <![CDATA[<color=orange>escape pod</color>]]> crashed as we tried to flee this place, destroying our movement and communication capabilities in the process.
		</Text>
	</TextBlock>
	<TextBlock>
		<ID>2</ID>
		<Text>
			SECCA: We’ve held out as long as we could here, but this pod’s supply of breathable air is nearly depleted, and the anglerfish attack more and more frequently.
		</Text>
	</TextBlock>
	<TextBlock>
		<ID>3</ID>
		<Text>
			SECCA: Our best chance at survival is to return to the <![CDATA[<color=orange>Vessel</color>]]> to either repair the damage or, more probably, await rescue.
		</Text>
	</TextBlock>
	<TextBlock>
		<ID>4</ID>
		<Text>
			ESCALL: Secca, is the message finished? The <![CDATA[<color=orange>Vessel</color>]]>’s beacon is already growing fainter; it will be gone in a matter of hours. We need to leave here, quickly.
		</Text>
	</TextBlock>

